    <h1>Product and technology</h1>
</div>

<p class="lead">
    Mon Mould factory is engaged in injection mould manufacturing.
    We are designing moulds according to customer drawings and/or samples.
    The factory applies quality control.
    When mould get ready we perform a trial it and send moulded samples to the customer.
    We perform finishing processing and preparation for delivery after get confirmation from the customer.
</p>
<p>
    The factory is equipped with modern processing equipment.
    Designing and manufacturing of products is carried out by experienced specialists.<br>
</p>
