<p>
    We are performing quality control during the whole manufacturing cycle from mould design to packing before delivery
</p>
<ul>
    <li>Design checking and mold flow analysis</li>
    <li>Inspection for mould material hardness</li>
    <li>Inspection for size of cavity and core</li>
    <li>Inspection the whole mould before and after assembly</li>
    <li>Mould trial on injection moulding and send samples to customer</li>
    <li>Final inspection and package control before delivery</li>
</ul>
<p>
    As the main CAD/CAM/CAE tools we are using actual version of NX Unigraphics software.
    Due to this we can carry out a full cycle of design and production of the product and exchange documents with the customer.
    You can send us 3D models (or 2D drawings) of the required product.
    In this case we recommend using common file formats: DXF, DWG, PRT, SAT, IGES, STEP and others.
</p>
<p>
    While designing a mould we perform mould flow control to avoid defects on final products.
</p>
